Subject: Re: [T2] re:Tow Bar Advice

A 1976 Type 2 with a manual is rated to tow:

trailer with brakes: 2645 lbs
trailer w/o brakes: 1322 lbs
tongue weight: 110 lbs

http://www.thesamba.com/vw/archives/manuals/76bus/76II-64.jpg

And although it only has 67 H.P, it has 101 ft/lbs of torque!

Greg U
